<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu chawnban hatah kinga'n la,
 Hun panpih ina...panpih ina;
 A hehpih zuou ngeilo na gin chun,
 La'n na lung dim ina.

[V2]
 A khut' kinga'n, A hehpih gingcha'n,
 A khut' kinga'n, A lungsiet a lang;'
 A khut' kinga'n, Chunglam In enin,
 Hukdampa khutah kinga'n.

[V3]
 2. Isu chawnban hatah kinga'n la,
 Lam hih vak ina...hih vak ina;
 A hun puihna'h kipakin zuiin,
 A tawngdam nem ngaiin.

[V4]
 3. Isu chawnban hatah kinga'n la,
 Na dahna hun puo'n...dahna hun puo'n;
 Na lunggil gikpuok gik takmai chu,
 Lalpa pie'n paucham in.

[V5]
 4. Isu chawnban hatah kinga'n la,
 Amah chu muongin...Amah muong in;
 A lunggil hehpihna'n a dim hi,
 A mit a thim ngei puoi.

[V6]
 5. Isu chawnban hatah kinga'n la,
 Na thilkhawk cheng...Ama'n hun pie'na;
 Hukdampa banga pawmte dingin,
 Guol taktak chuh ahi.</lyrics>
<title>LEAN UPON HIS ARMS</title>
</song>